\n更重要既係唔好將睇返黎既野當係金科玉律<br />\n而要培養到一套自己習慣既講野同回應方法<br />\n<br />\n例如除左共識題外 我會習慣性<br />\n1)先&quot;歸納&quot;人地既論點 再 加兩句&quot;建議&quot;或者&quot;評論&quot;<br />\n2)比自己既point 一般黎講會出簡單例子(15秒內)去扣題 <br />\n3)比較唔同選項(近年較多3揀1/2揀1) 用同一比較點去比較<br />\n<br />\n講出黎容易 老老實實周圍都係咁教<br />\n但與其你再去不停&quot;溫notes&quot; &quot;學技巧&quot; 其實學既永遠都係個老師既野<br />\n而無法轉化成自己既學養 <br />\n真正要做到既係&quot;practice makes perfect&quot;<br />\n<br />\n例如第1點 單係 &quot;歸納論點&quot;已經唔容易<br />\n你要做到既係用三言兩語概括到對方成分鐘既廢up(無錯 出面去考試d人都是1999的)<br />\n<br />\n我句句式就係&quot;嗯 咁剛才A同學就從「XX」方向探討 我都認同佢係「YY」角度上既作用既 而且仲可以「ZZ」添 確係相當好既優勢 而我就再想從「KK」方面分享下我既睇法喎&quot;<br />\n<br />\n咁呢D要背唔難 但係要去到你真係條條題目都有能力反射 仲要概括得好 其實就唔容易<br />\nXX YY ZZ KK 呢D應用點 都要長期經驗(所謂&quot;語感&quot;)去反射<br />\n呢D野 並唔係&quot;溫書&quot; &quot;上連登睇教學&quot;可以做到  而係要確確實實地從實戰訓練出黎<br />\n我教書其實SKILLS 一堂就教晒 但係要令學生可以實戰用得返出黎<br />\n就需要大量既說話練習了"},{"pid":"35eee0383b458ccac2a8543279ac7ec8d233b050","tid":735528,"uid":137521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6238b02a4e1368141519aab4d8bccc57decbcc7","tid":735528,"uid":18265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:12:52.000Z","msg":"鵠巴我喺舊登就睇緊你嘅中文心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:24:41.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然睇完最後都係得條5<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但係閱讀都因為睇左有5**<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b327cbfe33a3339aa52123c0b1c67df68a010924","tid":735528,"uid":103005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35eee0383b458ccac2a8543279ac7ec8d233b050","tid":735528,"uid":137521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6238b02a4e1368141519aab4d8bccc57decbcc7","tid":735528,"uid":18265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:12:52.000Z","msg":"鵠巴我喺舊登就睇緊你嘅中文心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:24:41.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然睇完最後都係得條5<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但係閱讀都因為睇左有5**<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:26:57.000Z","msg":"多謝比面 好似已經係5年前既POST了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd3ed87b01a68295bb8613e8e86ade4f23d54aa","tid":735528,"uid":103005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f0896d4a750ef1db2d63d12f549f91e4ce49eb3","tid":735528,"uid":53309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:20:18.000Z","msg":"中文要浸個方面應該點入手？例如多睇書抄低d靚句？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:27:25.000Z","msg":"呢個都想分享下 不過一匹布咁長 等我組織下先"},{"pid":"7fed164bf89b0ea699daabba77fe975e3e3df9e6","tid":735528,"uid":53309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fd3ed87b01a68295bb8613e8e86ade4f23d54aa","tid":735528,"uid":103005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f0896d4a750ef1db2d63d12f549f91e4ce49eb3","tid":735528,"uid":53309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:20:18.000Z","msg":"中文要浸個方面應該點入手？例如多睇書抄低d靚句？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:27:25.000Z","msg":"呢個都想分享下 不過一匹布咁長 等我組織下先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:28:22.000Z","msg":"期待鵠巴分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4adb766a9d470f26f6ad071a088347e552abef7","tid":735528,"uid":103005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:28:50.000Z","msg":"咦 太耐無上連登 是否開錯左台?<br />\n